{"tid":258810,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人食過上環街市瑞記既西多？","createTime":"2017-05-26T12:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T14:34:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34f4e3bbb537b305993799048d7671c08ab3a9ca","tid":258810,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"棠哥帶你食好西⋯⋯⋯多。<br />\n西多，原名法蘭西多士，但喺法國食唔到嘅多士，係香港人茶餐廳必食之一，想嘗甜頭又既冇菠蘿油咁罪惡感，想過口癮頂肚餓又冇餐蛋麵咁heavy。<br />\n幾十年來，西多只屬茶檔茶餐廳專美，喺大餐廳酒店叫西多，話之你Peninsula，總之嘥氣。<br />\n食勻全港，講西多我數上環街市熟食中心的瑞記排第二，睇怕唔敢有人爭第一，咁堅？係！<br />\n西多必經油炸，但哩檔獨有炮製方法，麵包蘸滿蛋漿後輕炸，火喉控制恰到好處，多士四周邊皮位脆口惹味，中間蛋香馥郁甘甜，入口軟脆兼得，至於糖漿一概欠奉，歎西多識食只會食煉奶，夾杯淡奶茶，真係識飲識食天下無敵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/StephenAuKamTong/posts/1425359594193872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FStephenAuKamTong%2Fposts%2F1425359594193872&d=594jwF06iYRaoK%2BpvQI4GBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7d6dcc8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/StephenAuKamTong/posts/1425359594193872</a><br />\n<br />\n堅唔堅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9e6ac82aa754eeb2c30c6246912d2f032b0132","tid":258810,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用煎既做法幾好<br />\n不過我唔鍾意用煉奶<br />\n泗益啱我d<br />\n<br />\n利申:兩間都幾年無去"},{"pid":"894a2992b72bd85973e4b9dfa04c2888e530fc98","tid":258810,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"西多係好食過一般茶記, 但係唔多甜, 落好少煉奶<br />\n杯奶茶好普通"},{"pid":"5dadb556aa75c14ce3f1319f9c94d8990ee9f86d","tid":258810,"uid":36184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"好好食，奶茶好香滑<br />\n我自己通常叫蛋牛包多蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9c61cc30c383cc6eabc1983f214b559846f625","tid":258810,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9aeea9caa7252ae8c6535b6d59fbad9591329cf8","tid":258810,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad91ffd7f7a2dd97097d03676b15191e18e2df00","tid":258810,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\nhi 記唔記得我？"},{"pid":"bc7d9860cb6cb51c002fe6ec672a97bf6adce1c7","tid":258810,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T19:43:14.000Z","msg":"應該問有冇人無食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢間野 幾年前都已經講緊"},{"pid":"943d1ea24f0a5341e9394ea8af0812cdc1d1d9c5","tid":258810,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:03:25.000Z","msg":"好食呀"},{"pid":"d39b390080ae3cdf712033b3f374e557da65aa34","tid":258810,"uid":390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T18:47:52.000Z","msg":"屌今日食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西多真心食過咁多間<br />\n瑞記幾特別同好香口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奶茶都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：孤陋寡聞 唔係食家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60beba0aeeb7faa7db5f49cae8da7668e9753773","tid":258810,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"瑞記又貴，質數一般狗也不屌"},{"pid":"a11052440a02e22d0edf081154d028e3d7708a25","tid":258810,"uid":114976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瑞記又貴，質數一般狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\n係貴左小小 但幾好食"},{"pid":"32ff8cd85a9d610a8b4c6e3d9f3360012443459f","tid":258810,"uid":114967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"上次食完 樽奶茶伏到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7ce8fa02c00e56dbb362f883d3e46a141ae35e","tid":258810,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"堅尼地城 誠記 可以一試"},{"pid":"ff48c97934cfba7ec2e1a5772ec2452c358a36dc","tid":258810,"uid":78481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"好食"},{"pid":"882141706bac8563031b63c543d846bb50049aba","tid":258810,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次食完 樽奶茶伏到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好甜"}]}